title: Lady Red Raiders Continue Undefeated
text:
Lady Red Raiders Continue Undefeated   8, 2015 at 6:40 AM   8, 2015 at 6:59 AM EDT 
The Lowville Lady Red Raiders continue undefeated after a girls' Frontier League soccer contest Wednesday against South Jefferson. Lowville shut out the Lady Spartans 1-0.
